Multimodal Model Comparison Table. Models: GPT-4o, Claude 4 Vision, Gemini 2.5 Pro, Llama 4 90B. Columns: Modalities, Vision Resolution, Price (Input/M tokens), Strengths. Rows with data and color coding. GPT-4o: Text/Image/Audio, 512x512-4096x4096, $2.50/M, General purpose. Claude 4 Vision: Text/Image, 8192x8192, $3.00/M, Document analysis. Gemini 2.5 Pro: Text/Image/Audio/Video, Native resolution, $1.25/M, Large context. Llama 4 90B: Text/Image, 1024x1024, Open Source, Self-hosted. German labels.